accommodation paddock
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:2
Definition:a holding paddock near an outstation, a country road or saleyards, in which to house stock temporarily.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
